Subject: drm/amdgpu: initialize the vmid_wait with the stub fence
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 48e9fbd1a28480caf2ac5ec6fcb79ac221735c5d
